#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.216:1.1"
msgid "… pe … Micchāājīvo hoti, micchāvāyāmo hoti, micchāsati hoti, micchāsamādhi hoti … pe … sammāājīvo hoti, sammāvāyāmo hoti, sammāsati hoti, sammāsamādhi hoti. "
msgstr "“Someone with four qualities is cast down to hell. … wrong livelihood, wrong effort, wrong mindfulness, and wrong immersion. Someone with four qualities is raised up to heaven. … right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
